i metro stations to open in April|publisher=[[Kathimerini]]|accessdate=25 March 2013}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n[[Category:Athens Metro stations]]\n[[Category:Railway stations opened in 2013]]\n\n{{Greece-railstation-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox station \n| name          = {{Infobox station/Header OASA|mode=M|line_1=M2|native_name=\u0391\u03bd\u03b8\u03bf\u03cd\u03c0\u03bf\u03bb\u03b7|name=Anthoupoli}}\n| type          = \n| style         = \n| image         =20140622-Anthoupoli-62D304 (7872).jpg\n| image_caption = Station platforms\n| address       = [[Thivon Street]], [[Athens]]\n| country       = [[Greece]]\n| coordinates   = {{Coord|38|01|01|N|23|41|30|E|type:railwaystation_region:GR-I|display=inline,title}}\n| line          = {{OASA icons|M2}} \n| other         = \n| structure     = Underground\n| platform      = 2\n| depth         = \n| levels        = 3\n| tracks        = 2\n| parking       = \n| bicycle       = \n| baggage_check = \n| opened        = 6 April 2013\n| closed        = \n| rebuilt       = \n| electrified   = \n| ADA           = \n| code          =\n| owned         =\n| operator      = Statheres Sygkoinonies S.A.\n| zone          = \n| smartcardname =\n| smartcardstatus =\n| former        = \n| passengers    = \n| pass_year     = \n| pass_percent  = \n| pass_system   = \n| mpassengers   = \n| services      = {{s-rail|title=OASA Metro}}\n{{s-line|system=OASA Metro|line=M2|previous=|next=Peristeri|type2=Elliniko}}\n| map_locator   = \n| web           = \n}}\n'''Anthoupoli metro station''' is the northern terminal station of  [[Athens Metro]] [[Line 2 (Athens Metro)|Line 2]] since the Peristeri extension in April 2013.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ametro.gr/page/default.asp?la=2&id=381 |title=AttikoMetro Inside - Peristeri |date=7 September 2012 |publisher=Attiko Metro S.A. |accessdate=3 October 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107083818/http://www.ametro.gr/page/default.asp?id=381&la=2 |archiveda